# Completion Gates

A task is complete only after relevant verification passes.

## Scala tasks

When Scala code is changed, run all of:

```bash
GITHUB_ACTIONS=TRUE sbt scalafmtAll Test/compile scalafmtAll
```

And also:
- Compile changed files/modules with Metals MCP compile tools when available.
- Report what was verified and what remains unverified.

## Non-Scala tasks

- Run the smallest relevant checks (lint/typecheck/tests) for touched areas.
- Do not claim "done" if checks were skipped; state why and what to run next.

## Completion signal

Before final handoff, provide:
1. What changed.
2. What was verified.
3. Any residual risk or follow-up.
